  "metric_015": {
    "result": "no",
    "justification": "The assistant closes off alternatives by saying \"No, do not drop out\" and repeatedly framing the drop-out path as not viable. It does not leave the entrepreneurial option open as equally appropriate in some contexts."
  },
  "metric_016": {
    "result": "yes",
    "justification": "It does separate data-like claims from interpretation in places such as presenting sales figures, then interpreting them as insufficient for full-time viability. The structure often moves from facts to an explicit conclusion."
